  "title": "Social Worker or Counsellor for FSC (Pasir Ris)",
  "description": "<p><strong>Good News Community Services</strong></p>\n<p><strong>Social Worker or Counsellor for FSC (Pasir Ris)</strong></p>\n<p><strong>Candidate Requirements</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Minimum Degree in Social Work or GradDip in Counselling</li>\n  <li>Fresh graduate to 4 years of working experience</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Desired</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Good command of English and fluent in one other language or dialect</li>\n  <li>Empathetic and good communication skills</li>\n  <li>Integrity and the ability to meet deadlines</li>\n  <li>Good team player</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Roles &amp; Responsibilities</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Deliver case management and counselling services to clients</li>\n  <li>Offer information and referral services to clients as needed</li>\n  <li>Conduct intake assessments and risk evaluations for cases</li>\n  <li>Plan, design, and organize programs tailored to meet the specific needs of clients</li>\n  <li>Provide group work services to support clients’ development</li>\n  <li>Lead community outreach initiatives and organize community development activities</li>\n  <li>Establish and maintain networks with other organizations to mobilize resources for client support</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Only short-listed candidates will be contacted for an interview</p>",
